Evolutionary game theory on scale free networks

This is an implementation (in the Chapel programming language) of the 
prisoner's dilemma on scale free networks, based on [1].

Note: this also serves as a first introduction to Chapel for me.

Author: Roald Frederickx <roald.frederickx@gmail.com>


References:
[1] Santos, F. C., Pacheco, J. M., 2005. Scale-free networks provide a 
    unifying framework for the emergence of cooperation. Phys. Rev. Lett. 
    95, 098104.

